    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/497f6b3ab2445e98e93bbc534f1f8c0a.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=1170 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/497f6b3ab2445e98e93bbc534f1f8c0a.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/497f6b3ab2445e98e93bbc534f1f8c0a.mp4?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《主机保卫队》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—复古未来主义策略游戏。一种计算机病毒已渗透到“占星师”研究设施中。建筑群里的大多数机器人都被感染。你需要指挥一个由4个原型机组成的部队保卫主机。你将不得不击退突袭，消灭制造者，下载珍贵数据，清除受感染的节点等等在通往设置最深区域路途中的其他工作。克服装备的限制和缺点，创建强大的组合。用多种战术摧毁对手：过热，腐蚀，吸收伤害并回敬对方。不要只依赖一种策略——单一策略很可能被敌人破解。最重要的是：保护主机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/2ad78f6b2cef9e7d4b19fcd307c90c86.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/2ad78f6b2cef9e7d4b19fcd307c90c86.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/2ad78f6b2cef9e7d4b19fcd307c90c86.mp4?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/ce0044d68de05cbabfa8abff7a2c4b8b.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=1170 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/ce0044d68de05cbabfa8abff7a2c4b8b.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>* 复古风格：</strong>80年代绘图结合时尚复古音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/c3ab0122f0c41ad399f8a1dc8d66acef.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/c3ab0122f0c41ad399f8a1dc8d66acef.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/c3ab0122f0c41ad399f8a1dc8d66acef.mp4?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>* 多种战术：</strong>用过热杀死机器人，用子弹狂射，用强力射击将其一击毙命，或用状态效果使其瘫痪——游戏在设计时考虑了许多可行的策略。<br><br><strong>* 组建你的部队：</strong>与必须组合套牌的纸牌游戏类似，在《<strong>主机保卫队</strong>》中，你必须将具有独特属性的装备组合在一起以创建无敌部队。通过强大的策略来弥补装备缺陷！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/6ee94e80ceec24eee6e744f82e3da026.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/6ee94e80ceec24eee6e744f82e3da026.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/6ee94e80ceec24eee6e744f82e3da026.mp4?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>* 独特的对手：</strong>请注意，敌人不会停滞不前。每个单位都有在部队中发挥独特作用，每个单位都有能力应对某些策略。运用策略选择目标，出奇制胜，不然就有被打败的危险。<br><br><strong>* 程序等级：</strong>手工制作的房间与程序级别的生成相结合。不同任务有不同的目标，并有独特的条件。接受挑战，还是被敌人远远甩在身后？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/fa7b237ed8aa1859ef03ba996dbcb5e5.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/fa7b237ed8aa1859ef03ba996dbcb5e5.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/fa7b237ed8aa1859ef03ba996dbcb5e5.mp4?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>* 递进系统：</strong>游戏不会以一胜一负结束！解锁新的单位，每个单位都有一套独特的升级和起始物品。解锁新物品以支持你的新策略。了解“占星师”中的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/715229907ccdb6537db669b2f5d0aa8f.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/715229907ccdb6537db669b2f5d0aa8f.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/715229907ccdb6537db669b2f5d0aa8f.mp4?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/a27580de15be16c9e792ece7d4168d13.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=1170 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/a27580de15be16c9e792ece7d4168d13.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>订阅我们的 <strong>Discord</strong>，以便获得《主机保卫队》的更新消息。在这里可以分享评论与建议，还可以与我们的团队共同讨论下一部游戏制作_</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/6a81b8d1d5865bd408bcec891bd8cac1.poster.avif?t=1771855209\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184810/extras/6a81b8d1d5865bd408bcec891bd8cac1.webm?t=1771855209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  </p>",
